name: Cellnetrix
tag_list: smart-card, sim, usim, security-token, java-card, mobile-applications
overview:
Cellnetrix is an R&D company focused on the development of software which makes wireless mobility and Internet services more reliable and secure.

The company implements software on different embedded platforms, first of all, for universal subscriber identity modules (USIM) for various mobile networks such as GSM, UMTS or CDMA, as well as WLAN and Internet, provides secure value-added mobile applications and full-scale Over-the-Air post-issuance management services for (U)SIM and R-UIM card based on proprietary OTA platform.

Embedded software solutions delivered by the company are based on the de facto industry standards maintained by Open Mobile Alliance, 3GPP, ETSI and Global Platform and use widely adopted Sun’s Java programming language.
